OL,3,CMinisters to prioritise compensation
OL,4,Cbid by man wrongly jailed for 38 years
OL,6,FThe Government has pledged to
OL,7,Fprioritise any bid for compensation by
OL,8,Fa man who spent 38 years in prison
OL,9,Fafter wrongly being convicted of
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FSpeaking in Parliament, justice
OL,13,Fminister Lord Ponsonby of Shulbrede
OL,14,Fsaid he would "encourage" Peter
OL,15,FSullivan, 68, to seek a payout.
