OL,3,CMinisters to prioritise compensation
OL,4,Cbid by man wrongly jailed for 38 years
OL,6,FThe previous chairwoman Helen Pitcher
OL,7,Fresigned in January over the
OL,8,Fcontroversy sparked by Mr Malkinson's
OL,9,Fcase, claiming she had been
OL,10,Fscapegoated.
OL,12,FMr Sullivan, who to date has spent
OL,13,Fmore of his life in prison than free,
OL,14,Ffinally had his name cleared last week
OL,15,Fafter decades protesting his innocence.
OL,17,FCrucial DNA evidence was finally
OL,18,Funearthed due to scientific advances
OL,19,Flast year, showing it was another
OL,20,Funknown man who raped and murdered 21-
OL,21,Fyear-old Diane Sindall in 1986.
