OL,4,Cbid by man wrongly jailed for 38 years
OL,6,FIndependent crossbencher Baroness
OL,7,FDeech, a former chairwoman of the Bar
OL,8,FStandards Board and a member of the
OL,9,FLaw Commission, said: "Does it not add
OL,10,Finsult to injury that after a person
OL,11,Fhas wasted the whole of their life in
OL,12,Fjail, that they don't get immediate
OL,13,Fcompensation as soon as they are
OL,14,Freleased?"
